I would like to recommend to you a novel called Journey to the West. It is one of the most famous science fiction novels in Chinese history. Hundreds of millions of people have watched it and gave it a high rating. So I believe it is It's worth seeing.
In addition, this is a very good book to teach you how to deal with difficulties and solve problems. The book describes the master and apprentices united and helped each other, experienced a lot of hardships along the way, and fought against the demons, and finally completed the goal , Got the Buddhist scriptures.
I believe you can learn a lot from it.

